body:
I've just tested the old PR #1241 against the master, and the problems reported in the comments are now gone. With that fix, I also see REEF jobs exit cleanly even without explicit `System.exit()` call at the end of `REEFLauncher.main()`. Hence, it can probably close [REEF-1715](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/REEF-1715) issue as well, although I would give it more testing first.

I think we should reopen (and merge) #1241 and close #1270; logging improvements from #1270 can be pulled in separately as another JIRA issue.

@markusweimer @shouhengyi-microsoft WDYT?
